"overview.operator_snapshot.body" = "Start in `Nodes` to run the real `/a2a/hello` handshake, keep the node alive through authenticated `/a2a/heartbeat` polling, move to `Skills` to manage the Skill Store, use `Services` to inspect marketplace listings or publish your own callable agent service, then open `Graph` to query your paid EvoMap knowledge graph directly from macOS.";
